  * d/*.upstart: Fix upstart jobs.
  * d/pydist-overrides: Correct pymongo and wsme package names.
  * d/control: moved mongodb recommends to api and collector
    packages (LP: #1131627).
  * d/files: copying pipeline.yaml.
  * d/control: fixed typo (LP: #1140309).

